== Events == * [[:en:Tenpyō-hōji|Tenpyō-hōji]] 8th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:764|764]] [[:en:November 6|November 6]] ） - [[:en:Emperor Junnin|Emperor Junnin]] が[[:en:Fujiwara no Nakamaro Rebellion|Fujiwara no Nakamaro Rebellion]] に加わったとして廃され、孝謙上皇が重祚、第48代・[[:en:Empress Kōken|Emperor Shōtoku]] に * [[:en:Enkyō (Kamakura period)|Enkei]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1308|1308]] [[:en:November 22|November 22]] ） - [[:en:Tokuji|Tokuchi]] から{{ill|Enkei|ja|延慶|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enkei|qq=|1=Enkei (Japan)|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1306063}} に{{ill|Change of era|ja|改元|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Change of era|qq=|1=era change|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11498853}} * {{ill|Zheng Tong (Ming)|ja|正統 (明)|lt=Zheng Tong|lt_ja=正統|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Zheng Tong (Ming)|qq=|1=Zhengtong Era|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q840384}} 11th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1446|1446]] [[:en:October 28|October 28]] ） - [[:en:Korea|Joseon]] の[[:en:Sejong the Great|Sejong]] が訓民正音（[[:en:Hangul|Hangul]] ）を公布 * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 3rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1870|1870]] [[:en:November 2|November 2]] ） - [[:en:Iwasaki Yatarō|Iwasaki Yatarō]] が{{ill|Tosa Kaiseisha|ja|土佐開成社|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tosa Kaiseisha|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} を開設。{{ill|Mitsubishi zaibatsu|ja|三菱財閥|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mitsubishi zaibatsu|qq=|1=Mitsubishi zaibatsu|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q10866745}} の起源
== Births == * [[:en:Bunsei|Bunsei]] 10th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1827|1827]] [[:en:November 27|November 27]] ） - {{ill|Yamauchi Toyonobu|ja|山内豊信|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamauchi Toyonobu|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 山内容堂|1=Yamauchi Toyoshige|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q711001}} （[[:en:Yamauchi Toyoshige|Yamauchi Yūdō]] ）、14代[[:en:Tosa Domain|Tosa Domain]] 主（+ [[:en:1872|1872]] ） * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 9th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1838|1838]] [[:en:November 25|November 25]] ） - [[:en:Yasuda Zenjirō|Yasuda Zenchirō]] 、[[:en:Yasuda zaibatsu|Yasuda zaibatsu]] 創始（+ [[:en:1921 (2021 film)|1921]] ） * 天保15th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1844|1844]] [[:en:November 18|November 18]] ） - [[:en:Yamada Akiyoshi|Yamada Akenori]] 、[[:en:Politician|Politician]] （+ [[:en:1892|1892]] ）
