* {{ill|Zheng Tong (Ming)|ja|正統 (明)|lt=Zheng Tong|lt_ja=正統|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Zheng Tong (Ming)|1=Zhengtong Era|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q840384}} 11th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}   {{ill|1446|en|1446|WD=Q6430|lt=1446|1=1446}} {{ill|October 28|en|October 28|WD=Q2952|lt=October 28|1=October 28}} ） - {{ill|Korea|en|Korea|WD=Q18097|lt=Joseon|1=Korea}} の{{ill|Sejong the Great|en|Sejong the Great|WD=Q37682|lt=Sejong|1=Sejong the Great}} が訓民正音（{{ill|Hangul|en|Hangul|WD=Q8222|lt=Hangul|1=Hangul}} ）を公布
